source.name: ~ Measure 13 : Percentage of the Nonelderly Population with Health Insurance Coverage by State
source.description: Please note that a 3-year moving-average merge of CPS data is required in order to reduce sampling errors to create comparable state estimates.  These estimates were constructed using years 2008-2010.
